    "title": "OYO Rooms Digital Technologies is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "Join the OYO Rooms Digital Technologies family as a Guest Relations Manager in Madurai. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout OYO Rooms Digital Technologies:\nOYO Rooms Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with OYO Rooms Digital Technologies!",
